task.summary:
Started porting to 1.4.6.
Added APIs, IDEA project. Added after build hook to handle forge and FML configs and textures.
Created more packages to make structure nicer.

Some work on power api.
Fixed name of proxy.
Added option in config to enable multidimensional behaviour of home stones (still occasionally buggy, disabled by default).
Added glass of milk, updated crafting handler to support direct output items transfer to a player.
Modified/added food effects of most foods (fixed extreme poison effect of new raw meats).
